  <brief_title>Effect of Aerobic or Resistance Exercise on the Endothelial Response in Post-acute Myocardial Infarction Patients Submitted to Angioplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Aerobic or Resistance Exercise on the Endothelial Response in Post-acute Myocardial Infarction Patients Submitted to Angioplasty: Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
